WEBVTT

00:31.481 --> 00:32.965
GOOD NEWS, EVERYONE.

00:33.033 --> 00:35.862
I'VE INVENTED A DEVICE
WHICH ALLOWS YOU

00:35.930 --> 00:38.930
TO OPERATE EQUIPMENT
FROM GREAT DISTANCES.

00:39.000 --> 00:40.896
I CALL IT THE FINGLONGER.

00:40.965 --> 00:42.585
OBSERVE.

00:42.655 --> 00:45.171
AND... HERE WE GO...

00:45.240 --> 00:48.067
THERE.

00:48.137 --> 00:49.344
[ All Gasping ]

00:49.412 --> 00:50.689
PRETTY LONG, EH?

00:50.758 --> 00:51.930
YEAH, IT'S REALLY LONG

00:52.000 --> 00:54.137
BUT WHAT DID YOU JUST
TURN ON WITH IT?

00:54.206 --> 00:57.206
OH, THAT'S JUST
THE WHAT-IF MACHINE I INVENTED.

00:57.274 --> 00:59.274
YOU POSE IT A "WHAT IF" QUESTION

00:59.344 --> 01:02.965
AND IT GENERATES A VIDEO
SIMULATION OF WHAT WOULD HAPPEN.

01:03.033 --> 01:05.448
DOES IT REALLY WORK?OF COURSE IT WORKS.

01:05.516 --> 01:07.171
IT'S JUST NOT
VERY LONG.

01:07.240 --> 01:09.965
OOH, OOH, I WANT
TO AXE IT A QUESTION.

01:10.034 --> 01:11.965
AS A ROBOT LIVING
AMONG HUMANS

01:12.034 --> 01:15.000
I'VE NEVER REALLY FELT
ACCEPTED AT PARTIES

01:15.067 --> 01:16.655
OR NUDE BEACHES.

01:16.724 --> 01:20.240
SO, I'VE ALWAYS
SECRETLY WONDERED...

01:20.310 --> 01:23.067
WHAT IF I WAS 500 FEET TALL?

01:23.137 --> 01:25.137
LET'S WATCH, SHALL WE?

01:37.516 --> 01:38.655
[ Loud Belch ]

01:38.723 --> 01:40.516
MY WORK HERE IS DONE.

01:53.758 --> 01:58.826
[ Black Sabbath's
"Iron Man" Playing ]

02:03.965 --> 02:08.550
AW, I'M SO LONELY
SINCE I CAME TO THE FUTURE.

02:08.620 --> 02:10.033
WILL YOU BE MY FRIEND?

02:10.103 --> 02:11.310
[ Angry Quack ]OW!

02:15.448 --> 02:17.310
[ Groans ]

02:17.378 --> 02:19.275
AW!

02:19.343 --> 02:20.343
[ Gasps ]

02:20.413 --> 02:21.896
WHO ARE YOU?

02:21.965 --> 02:25.413
I'M A BIG ROBOT
AND I WANT A BIG CEREAL.

02:25.481 --> 02:28.793
YOU, TOO?
WILL YOU BE MY FRIEND?

02:28.861 --> 02:30.826
PUT HER THERE, PAL.

02:32.206 --> 02:33.586
I MEANT YOUR WALLET.

02:33.655 --> 02:35.826
THREE, TWO, ONE, ZERO.♪ MMMBOP BA-DUBA-DOP ♪

02:35.896 --> 02:38.826
♪ BA-DU-BOP, BA-DU-DOP ♪

02:38.896 --> 02:41.688
♪ BA-DU-BOP, BA-DU-DOP ♪

02:41.758 --> 02:43.206
♪ YEAH, YEAH ♪

02:43.275 --> 02:45.481
♪ MMMBOP BA-DUBA-DOP ♪

02:45.550 --> 02:48.310
♪ BA-DU-BOP, BA-DU-DOP ♪

02:48.378 --> 02:50.240
♪ BA-DU-BOP, BA-DU-DOP ♪

02:50.310 --> 02:51.378
♪ WHOA, WHOA ♪

02:51.448 --> 02:53.758
♪ MMMBOP BA-DUBA-DOP ♪

02:53.826 --> 02:55.240
♪ BA-DU-BOP, BA-DU-DOP ♪

02:55.310 --> 02:59.655
♪ BA-DU-BOP, BA-DU-DOP ♪

02:59.723 --> 03:01.378
♪ WHOA, WHOA ♪

03:01.448 --> 03:03.793
♪ MMMBOP BA-DUBA-DOP... ♪

03:26.758 --> 03:29.620
AH, YEAH,
THAT CALMS THE SHAKES.

03:29.688 --> 03:30.931
HEY!

03:32.793 --> 03:34.861
[ Giggling ]

03:34.930 --> 03:36.413
OKAY, OKAY, COME ON NOW.

03:36.481 --> 03:39.171
STOP! THE ROBOT'S
NOT YOUR ENEMY.

03:39.240 --> 03:40.930
HE'S JUST A POOR,
MISUNDERSTOOD....

03:41.000 --> 03:42.103
[ Screaming ]

03:48.103 --> 03:49.275
[ Sniffing ]

03:49.343 --> 03:51.378
AW!

03:58.516 --> 04:00.033
WELL, THERE GOES
THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

04:00.103 --> 04:01.310
[ Loud Crashing ]

04:01.378 --> 04:02.758
THERE GOES ANOTHER
NEIGHBORHOOD.

04:02.826 --> 04:03.931
WE'RE JERKED.

04:04.000 --> 04:06.240
NOTHING CAN STOP
A MONSTER THAT BIG.

04:06.310 --> 04:08.965
NOTHING EXCEPT AN EVEN
EQUALLY BIG MONSTER.

04:09.033 --> 04:13.137
THIS IS A CHANCE TO TRY OUT
MY EXPERIMENTAL ENLARGING RAY

04:13.205 --> 04:15.137
BUT WE'LL NEED A GUINEA PIG.

04:17.862 --> 04:19.793
[ Sniffing ]

04:19.862 --> 04:21.964
WHAT'S THIS?

04:22.033 --> 04:24.033
TWO MEALS IN ONE WEEK?

04:24.103 --> 04:26.067
[ Noisy Chewing ]

04:27.379 --> 04:28.757
GOT YOU!SUCKER!

04:28.826 --> 04:31.033
FRIENDS, HELP!
A GUINEA PIG TRICKED ME.

04:32.240 --> 04:33.620
[ High-pitched Whirring ]

04:33.689 --> 04:35.930
WHAT?

04:38.620 --> 04:41.689
SO, NOW ZOIDBERG IS BIG, HUH?

04:41.757 --> 04:43.896
THAT'S MORE LIKE IT.

04:43.965 --> 04:47.379
WHO'S INTIMIDATING
WHO NOW, BIG CITY?

04:47.447 --> 04:50.310
HELLO, MR. CHASE MANHATTAN BANK.

04:50.379 --> 04:53.481
DENY MY CREDIT CARD
APPLICATION, WILL YOU?

04:53.550 --> 04:56.654
[ Roaring ]

04:56.723 --> 04:59.689
AH, THE FAMED
APOLLO THEATER.

04:59.757 --> 05:02.379
BOO ME OFF STAGE
ON OPEN-MIKE NIGHT, HUH?

05:02.447 --> 05:04.240
I'LL SHOW YOU.

05:04.310 --> 05:07.000
[ Roaring ]

05:07.067 --> 05:09.172
HEY, I CALLED
THIS CITY.

05:09.240 --> 05:11.137
QUIT TOUCHING
MY STUFF.

05:11.206 --> 05:12.723
TELL IT TO
THE CLAW.

05:12.793 --> 05:15.723
BITE MY COLOSSAL METAL ASS.

05:16.862 --> 05:18.793
[ People Screaming ]

05:19.862 --> 05:21.000
[ Loud Sucking ]

05:22.516 --> 05:24.516
[ Sputtering ]

05:49.103 --> 05:50.481
[ Loud Belch ]

05:52.447 --> 05:54.930
WHO WANTS LOBSTER BISQUE?

05:55.000 --> 05:56.447
HMM?

05:56.516 --> 05:58.240
[ Screaming ]

05:58.310 --> 06:01.550
[ Evil Laughter ]

06:01.620 --> 06:02.964
HEY, BENDER

06:03.033 --> 06:05.103
WANT TO MAKE SHRINKY DINKS?

06:05.172 --> 06:07.310
[ Roaring ]

06:07.379 --> 06:08.826
[ Yelling ]

06:08.896 --> 06:10.550
[ Gasping ]

06:11.689 --> 06:15.689
WHO PUT THIS IN HERE?

06:21.654 --> 06:24.310
NO!

06:27.826 --> 06:29.447
ARE YOU PEOPLE
SATISFIED?

06:29.516 --> 06:32.067
THIS GENTLE
VISITOR IS DYING

06:32.137 --> 06:35.516
AND WE'LL NEVER EVEN
KNOW WHY HE CAME.

06:35.586 --> 06:37.310
I'LL... TELL YOU...

06:37.379 --> 06:39.896
WITH MY FINAL BREATH.

06:39.965 --> 06:42.379
[ Muttering ]

06:42.447 --> 06:46.274
I CAME HERE
WITH A SIMPLE DREAM--

06:46.343 --> 06:50.516
A DREAM OF KILLING ALL HUMANS

06:50.586 --> 06:54.620
AND THIS IS HOW IT MUST END?

06:54.689 --> 07:00.103
WHO'S THE REAL
SEVEN-BILLION-TON
ROBOT MONSTER HERE?

07:00.172 --> 07:03.000
NOT... I.

07:05.067 --> 07:08.620
NOT... I.

07:08.689 --> 07:10.240
[ Gasps ]

07:12.067 --> 07:14.172
GOOD NIGHT, SWEET PRINCE.

07:16.516 --> 07:19.240
[ Announcer ]
INTERESTING STUFF.

07:19.310 --> 07:21.343
STAY TUNED FOR MORE:

07:28.033 --> 07:29.206
[ Farnsworth ]
WELL, LEELA,

07:29.274 --> 07:31.413
CARE TO GIVE THE
WHAT-IF MACHINE A WHIRL?

07:31.481 --> 07:32.793
MAYBE LATER.

07:32.862 --> 07:35.172
I MEAN, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO ASK ABOUT.

07:35.240 --> 07:37.172
COME ON, WOMAN,
JUST PICK SOMETHING.

07:37.240 --> 07:39.862
YEAH, BE MORE
IMPULSIVE, LIKE THIS.

07:42.379 --> 07:44.274
GO, MAN, GO.

07:45.586 --> 07:50.206
I CAN BE REALLY IMPULSIVE.
IT JUST TAKES ME AWHILE.

07:50.274 --> 07:52.033
[ Humming Tune ]

07:52.103 --> 07:53.447
ALL RIGHT, PROFESSOR,
LET'S DO IT.

07:53.516 --> 07:56.137
MAKE THAT MACHINE
SHOW ME WHAT WOULD HAPPEN

07:56.206 --> 07:58.103
IF I WAS A LITTLE
MORE IMPULSIVE.

07:58.172 --> 07:59.343
JUST A LITTLE.

08:01.137 --> 08:02.033
NOT TOO MUCH.

08:04.067 --> 08:07.413
HEY, GUYS, LOOK WHAT
I BOUGHT ON A WILD IMPULSE--

08:07.482 --> 08:09.033
NEW BOOTS.

08:09.103 --> 08:12.620
THEY'RE LIKE MY OLD ONES
BUT WITH A CRAZY GREEN STRIPE.

08:12.689 --> 08:13.964
WHOO!

08:14.033 --> 08:16.447
NEVER KNOW WHAT
I'M GOING TO DO NEXT.

08:16.516 --> 08:18.172
[ Humming Tune ]

08:18.240 --> 08:19.550
[ Sighs ]

08:19.620 --> 08:21.689
LEELA, COULD YOU COME
IN HERE FOR A MOMENT?

08:21.757 --> 08:24.447
I HAVE SOMETHING
IMPORTANT TO TELL YOU.

08:24.516 --> 08:27.137
I CAN'T LIVE FOREVER
AND I NEED AN HEIR--

08:27.206 --> 08:29.137
SOMEONE TO SPEND MY VAST RICHES

08:29.206 --> 08:33.172
AND TAKE CARE OF
MY MAN-EATING ANTEATERS
WHEN I'M GONE.

08:33.240 --> 08:35.724
[ Noisy Chewing ]

08:35.793 --> 08:38.481
THE OTHERS SIMPLY AREN'T
LEVELHEADED ENOUGH.

08:38.551 --> 08:40.826
THEY'RE TOO IMPULSIVE--
NOT LIKE YOU.

08:40.895 --> 08:45.000
NOT LIKE OLD, PREDICTABLE,
DULL-AS-DISHWATER LEELA.

08:45.067 --> 08:47.172
HELLO? NEW BOOTS.

08:47.240 --> 08:49.793
THAT'S WHY I'VE MADE YOU
MY SOLE HEIR.

08:49.861 --> 08:51.206
THE DAY I DIE

08:51.274 --> 08:53.826
YOU'LL BE A VERY
WEALTHY WOMAN.

08:53.895 --> 08:57.136
OH, MY, YES...
INCREDIBLY WEALTHY.

08:57.206 --> 08:59.102
THE DAY I DIE...

08:59.172 --> 09:00.826
BECAUSE YOU'RE
SO UN-IMPULSIVE.

09:02.344 --> 09:03.793
[ Karate Yell ]

09:03.861 --> 09:05.344
OH! HUH?

09:05.413 --> 09:07.758
[ Noisy Chewing ]

09:07.826 --> 09:09.654
OH, YOU'VE KILLED ME!

09:09.724 --> 09:10.965
YOU'VE KILLED ME!

09:11.033 --> 09:13.033
OH, GOD, WHAT HAVE I DONE?

09:13.102 --> 09:15.688
I JUST TOLD YOU.
YOU'VE KILLED ME!

09:15.758 --> 09:17.172
[ Noisy Chewing ]

09:19.895 --> 09:22.551
OKAY, JUST TRY
TO BE NONCHALANT.

09:22.620 --> 09:25.551
[ Whistling Tune ]

09:25.620 --> 09:27.931
ALL RIGHT, SO
YOU'RE NONCHALANT.

09:28.000 --> 09:30.000
QUIT RUBBING
OUR NOSES IN IT.

09:30.067 --> 09:32.136
SWEET GIANT ANTEATER
OF SANTA ANITA!

09:32.206 --> 09:35.102
THE PROFESSOR'S BEEN EATEN
BY GIANT ANTEATERS!

09:35.172 --> 09:36.379
OH!WHAT?!

09:36.447 --> 09:39.000
IF YOU ASK ME,
IT'S MIGHTY SUSPICIOUS.

09:39.067 --> 09:40.620
I'M GOING TO CALL THE POLICE...

09:40.688 --> 09:42.240
RIGHT AFTER
I FLUSH SOME THINGS.

09:42.309 --> 09:44.758
POLICE, BAH.
NOSY MEDDLERS.

09:44.826 --> 09:46.413
IT SO HAPPENS I HAVE

09:46.481 --> 09:50.861
MAIL-ORDER DEGREES
IN MURDEROLOGY AND MURDERONOMY.

09:50.931 --> 09:52.965
ZOIDBERG IS AFOOT.

09:53.033 --> 09:55.551
PERHAPS THE PROFESSOR'S
FILES CAN CLEAR THINGS UP.

09:55.620 --> 09:58.274
LET'S SEE, CITATION
FOR PUBLIC NUDITY

09:58.344 --> 10:00.586
CONSPIRACY TO COMMIT
PUBLIC NUDITY.

10:00.654 --> 10:03.206
AHA! A NEW WILL NAMING...

10:03.274 --> 10:04.551
[ Gasps ]

10:04.620 --> 10:06.067
YOUAS HIS SOLE HEIR!

10:06.136 --> 10:08.309
THAT DOESN'T PROVE
I KILLED HIM.

10:08.379 --> 10:10.654
IT'S A VIDEO WILL.
IT SHOWS YOU KILLING HIM.

10:15.758 --> 10:17.309
[ Karate Yells ]

10:17.379 --> 10:19.000
[ Hermes Screaming ]

10:19.067 --> 10:21.517
ALL RIGHT, ANTEATER NUMBER ONE,
WHO ARE YOU PROTECTING?

10:21.586 --> 10:23.136
IS IT ANTEATER NUMBER TWO?

10:23.206 --> 10:26.172
DON'T STICK YOUR TONGUE
OUT AT ME.

10:26.240 --> 10:28.274
I NEED A NAME. [ Snorting ]

10:28.344 --> 10:30.551
WHAT? HOW DO
YOU SPELL THAT?

10:30.620 --> 10:31.793
[ Chopping Sounds ]

10:31.861 --> 10:33.793
[ Hermes ]
WHAT ARE YOU
HACKING OFF?

10:33.861 --> 10:38.274
IS IT MY TORSO?
IT IS! MY PRECIOUS TORSO!

10:38.344 --> 10:41.688
HERMES, QUIET.
I'M DEDUCING THINGS.

10:41.758 --> 10:43.413
[ Garbage Disposal Running ]

10:43.481 --> 10:44.620
[ Grunting ]

10:44.688 --> 10:46.586
WHAT DO YOU GOT?
DISPOSAL TROUBLE?

10:46.654 --> 10:47.793
NO! EVERYTHING'S JUST--

10:47.861 --> 10:49.551
SURE IS SHOCKING ABOUT
THE PROFESSOR, HUH?

10:49.620 --> 10:52.206
AND NOW HERMES IS
MYSTERIOUSLY MISSING.

10:52.274 --> 10:54.688
ANYHOW, IT DOESN'T
AFFECT ME-- BENDER.

10:54.758 --> 10:55.861
HEY, WHAT'S THIS?

10:55.931 --> 10:57.620
HERMES' DREADLOCKS?
AND HIS ARM?

10:57.688 --> 10:59.136
LEELA, I'M SHOCKED.

10:59.206 --> 11:03.724
FOOD GOES IN THE DISPOSAL.
HAIR AND FLESH GO IN THE TRASH.

11:03.793 --> 11:05.965
I'M SORRY.
I COULDN'T STOP.

11:06.033 --> 11:07.067
WELL, WAIT.

11:07.136 --> 11:09.000
DON'T YOU CARE THAT
I MURDERED HERMES?

11:09.067 --> 11:10.309
NOT EVEN A LITTLE.

11:10.379 --> 11:12.067
THERE'S NOTHING WRONG
WITH MURDER

11:12.136 --> 11:14.379
JUST AS LONG AS YOU LET
BENDER WET HIS BEAK.

11:14.447 --> 11:15.758
YOU'RE BLACKMAILING ME?

11:15.826 --> 11:17.793
BLACKMAIL IS SUCH
AN UGLY WORD.

11:17.861 --> 11:19.102
I PREFER EXTORTION.

11:19.172 --> 11:21.102
THE "X" MAKES IT
SOUND COOL.

11:22.274 --> 11:24.206
PLEASE, HONEY,
I'M MADE OF METAL.

11:24.274 --> 11:26.688
LIKE YOU'RE REALLY GOING
TO HURT ME WITH A--

11:26.758 --> 11:29.240
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WITH THAT MICROWAVE?

11:31.586 --> 11:34.447
[ Blubbering ]

11:36.517 --> 11:38.172
[ Bell Dings ]

11:38.240 --> 11:40.206
OKAY, THAT'S IT.

11:40.274 --> 11:42.000
NO MORE KILLING.

11:42.067 --> 11:44.000
NEXT TIME YOU FEEL LIKE KILLING

11:44.067 --> 11:45.724
JUST HAVE A STICK OF GUM.

11:45.793 --> 11:48.344
NOW TO DISPOSE
OF THE BODY.

11:49.413 --> 11:51.413
HONK, HONK.

11:51.481 --> 11:54.758
WOW, SPORTY GO-CART, LEELA.
SO HIP AND SEXY.

11:54.826 --> 11:56.067
NOT LIKE YOU AT ALL.

11:57.274 --> 11:58.620
DO YOU HAVE ANY GUM?

11:58.688 --> 11:59.758
NO.

11:59.826 --> 12:02.102
[ Screaming ]

12:02.172 --> 12:05.172
[ Thunder Crashing ]

12:05.240 --> 12:07.240
[ Clock Chimes ]

12:10.033 --> 12:11.172
[ Noisy Chewing ]

12:11.240 --> 12:12.620
AH!

12:12.688 --> 12:14.102
THE GANG'S ALL HERE.

12:14.172 --> 12:15.379
WHO ARE YOU?

12:15.447 --> 12:16.586
SCRUFFY,
THE JANITOR.

12:16.654 --> 12:18.136
I'VE NEVER SEEN
YOU BEFORE.

12:18.206 --> 12:20.136
I'VE NEVER SEEN YOU
BEFORE, NEITHER.

12:20.206 --> 12:21.379
QUIET, PLEASE.

12:21.447 --> 12:23.965
I'VE CALLED YOU ALL HERE
TO THE PARLOR

12:24.033 --> 12:26.517
TO WATCH AS I GRADUALLY
SOLVE THE CRIME.

12:26.586 --> 12:29.861
ONE OF THE PEOPLE IN THIS ROOM
IS A BIG MURDERER.

12:29.931 --> 12:32.240
[ All Gasping ]

12:32.309 --> 12:33.965
[ Gasps ]

12:34.033 --> 12:36.861
YOU SEE, THE KILLER
LEFT ONE FATAL CLUE--

12:36.931 --> 12:39.895
THIS BOOT PRINT ON
THE PROFESSOR'S LAB COAT.

12:39.965 --> 12:41.379
UH... COULDN'T BE ME.

12:41.447 --> 12:42.688
I NEVER WEAR BOOTS.

12:42.758 --> 12:44.172
[ Loud Zipping ]

12:44.240 --> 12:45.274
SEE?

12:45.344 --> 12:47.586
EWW. WHAT SMELLS
LIKE BOOT FEET?

12:47.654 --> 12:50.136
THIS IS PREPOSTEROUS.

12:50.206 --> 12:51.758
OBVIOUSLY,
THE MURDERER IS--

12:51.826 --> 12:52.861
[ Metallic Scraping ]

12:52.931 --> 12:53.861
[ Splat ]

12:56.654 --> 12:58.447
MY NEXT CLUE CAME AT 4:15

12:58.517 --> 12:59.861
WHEN THE CLOCK STOPPED

12:59.931 --> 13:02.240
AND ANOTHER CAME
TWO HOURS LATER, AT 4:15

13:02.309 --> 13:04.447
WHEN I DISCOVERED
THE MURDERED BODY

13:04.517 --> 13:06.309
OF AMY'S DEAD, DECEASED CORPSE.

13:09.344 --> 13:11.758
SCRUFFY KNOWS
WHO KILLED THEM PEOPLE.

13:11.826 --> 13:14.067
IN SCRUFFY'S OPINION,
IT WERE--

13:14.136 --> 13:15.654
[ Metallic Scraping ]

13:15.724 --> 13:17.240
[ Casual Whistling ]

13:17.309 --> 13:19.620
SO... IT'S JUST AS I
SUSPECTED ALL ALONG.

13:19.688 --> 13:21.688
THE CRIME IS UNSOLVABLE.

13:21.758 --> 13:23.136
[ Yapping ]

13:25.758 --> 13:27.274
[ Yelping ]

13:31.517 --> 13:34.826
A LETTER FROM BENDER,
MY GOOD FRIEND.

13:34.895 --> 13:36.620
"DEAR DR. JERKBERG

13:36.688 --> 13:40.206
"IF YOU'RE READING THIS,
I'M ALREADY DEAD.

13:40.274 --> 13:44.033
"THE PERSON WHO
KILLED ME WAS-- WAS--"

13:44.102 --> 13:46.447
MY GOD.
IT CAN'T BE.

13:46.517 --> 13:47.895
THE MURDERER. IT WAS...

13:47.965 --> 13:49.240
[ Yawns ]

13:49.309 --> 13:50.447
I'M BORED.

13:50.517 --> 13:51.758
YOU'RE BORING,
ZOIDBERG.

13:51.826 --> 13:53.206
I'M GOING TO
GO WATCH TV.

13:53.274 --> 13:55.895
COULD YOU GET THE LIGHTS
ON YOUR WAY OUT?

13:58.240 --> 14:00.861
WHATCHA EATING?LOBSTER.

14:00.931 --> 14:02.309
YOU WANT SOME?SURE.

14:02.379 --> 14:04.309
YOU KNOW, I THINK
I FINALLY FIGURED OUT

14:04.379 --> 14:06.274
WHAT'S BEHIND ALL
THESE MYSTERIOUS DEATHS.

14:06.344 --> 14:07.481
REALLY?

14:07.551 --> 14:10.620
WAS PLANET EXPRESS BUILT
ON AN INDIAN GRAVEYARD?

14:10.688 --> 14:11.931
NO.NO?

14:12.000 --> 14:15.136
NO.[ Gasps ]
THEN... THEN...

14:15.206 --> 14:16.172
IT WAS YOU.

14:16.240 --> 14:18.102
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT CAME OVER ME.

14:18.172 --> 14:19.965
I KILLED ONE PERSON ON IMPULSE.

14:20.033 --> 14:22.586
THEN I HAD TO KILL
ANOTHER AND ANOTHER.

14:22.654 --> 14:24.620
WELL, THAT COVERS
THE FIRST THREE KILLINGS.

14:24.688 --> 14:27.688
AND NOW, TO MAKE SURE
YOUWON'T TALK...

14:27.758 --> 14:32.654
I'M GOING TO HAVE TO DO
SOMETHING REALLY IMPULSIVE.

14:34.586 --> 14:36.067
[ Contented Sigh ]

14:36.136 --> 14:37.240
SO, FRY...

14:37.309 --> 14:39.931
WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF THE IMPULSIVE NEW ME?

14:40.000 --> 14:41.274
I LIKE IT.

14:41.344 --> 14:45.654
GOOD, NOW LET ME
JUST GET THE LIGHTS.

14:45.724 --> 14:48.551
[ Screaming ]

14:48.620 --> 14:50.895
I REALLYLIKE IT.

14:54.931 --> 14:57.826
WHO ELSE HAS A QUESTION
FOR THE WHAT-IF MACHINE?

14:57.895 --> 14:59.172
SCRUFFY? FRY?

14:59.240 --> 15:00.620
I HAVE A QUESTION.

15:00.688 --> 15:02.517
WHAT IF BENDER
WAS REALLY GIANT?

15:02.586 --> 15:04.274
YOU IDIOT,
WE ALREADY SAW THAT.

15:04.344 --> 15:06.826
I KNOW, I LIKED IT.
I WANT TO SEE IT AGAIN.

15:06.895 --> 15:09.551
WE'RE NOT SEEING IT AGAIN.
ASK SOMETHING LESS STUPID.

15:09.620 --> 15:10.965
OH, ALL RIGHT,
HOW ABOUT THIS?

15:11.033 --> 15:13.102
WHAT IF I NEVER FELL
INTO THAT FREEZER DOODLE

15:13.172 --> 15:14.551
AND CAME TO THE FUTURE JIGGY?

15:14.620 --> 15:16.240
THAT QUESTION
IS LESS STUPID

15:16.309 --> 15:19.136
THOUGH YOU ASKED IT IN
A PROFOUNDLY STUPID WAY.

15:19.206 --> 15:23.172
WHAT WOULD HAPPEN IF FRY
NEVER CAME TO THE FUTURE?

15:25.793 --> 15:28.240
[ Noisemakers Blowing ]

15:33.826 --> 15:34.861
HELLO!

15:34.931 --> 15:37.033
PIZZA DELIVERY FOR, UH...

15:37.102 --> 15:38.688
I.C. WIENER?

15:38.758 --> 15:40.000
OH, CRUD.

15:43.586 --> 15:46.274
HERE'S TO ANOTHER
LOUSY MILLENNIUM.

15:49.895 --> 15:51.861
[ Toots ]

15:54.826 --> 15:55.895
OW!

15:57.102 --> 15:59.895
I SHOULD HAVE LEFT YOU
FLOATING IN THE TOILET.

16:04.895 --> 16:05.895
WHAT IS IT?

16:05.965 --> 16:07.895
IT APPEARS THAT
THE VERY FABRIC

16:07.965 --> 16:09.517
OF SPACE-TIME
HAS RIPPED.

16:09.586 --> 16:11.344
HEY, LOOK,
AN UGLY, SCARED GUY.

16:11.413 --> 16:12.861
BOO!

16:12.931 --> 16:14.517
[ Laughing ]

16:14.586 --> 16:17.517
[ Spooky Humming ]

16:17.586 --> 16:18.758
WHO ARE YOU MONSTERS?

16:18.826 --> 16:20.274
IS ONE OF YOU I.C. WIENER?

16:20.344 --> 16:23.206
IF THAT'S HIS PIZZA,
THEN I'M ICY WHATEVER.

16:30.517 --> 16:33.172
YOU BELIEVE ME
ABOUT THE MONSTERS,
RIGHT, MR. PANUCCI?

16:33.240 --> 16:35.861
THERE'S ONLY THREE
REAL MONSTERS, KID--

16:35.931 --> 16:37.931
DRACULA, BLACULA
AND SON OF KONG.

16:38.000 --> 16:42.000
NOW, QUIT PICKING YOUR NOSE
AND KNEAD THAT DOUGH.

16:42.067 --> 16:43.481
[ Sighs ]

16:44.654 --> 16:47.517
HEY, THE USUAL,
PROFESSOR HAWKING?

16:47.586 --> 16:50.067
[ Over Voice Box ]
NO, TODAY I'D LIKE
SOMETHING GOOD.

16:50.136 --> 16:53.517
[ Laughs ]
HAWKING, YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.
I'LL MAKE YOU THE USUAL.

16:53.586 --> 16:54.861
HEY, STEPHEN HAWKING.

16:54.931 --> 16:57.551
AREN'T YOU THAT PHYSICIST
THAT INVENTED GRAVITY?

16:57.620 --> 16:59.000
SURE, WHY NOT?

16:59.067 --> 17:00.517
LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

17:00.586 --> 17:03.274
HAS ANYONE EVER DISCOVERED
A HOLE IN NOTHING
WITH MONSTERS IN IT?

17:04.586 --> 17:05.758
'CAUSE IF I'M THE FIRST

17:05.826 --> 17:07.862
I WANT THEM TO CALL IT
A FRY HOLE.

17:07.931 --> 17:10.517
THERE IS NOTHING
TO BE CONCERNED ABOUT.

17:10.586 --> 17:13.136
I MUST GO.
THERE IS MUCH TO DO.

17:16.103 --> 17:18.000
HEY, HAWKING,
YOUR PIZZA'S READY.

17:18.067 --> 17:20.240
TOSS IT IN
THE GARBAGE.

17:24.964 --> 17:26.826
[ Hawking ]
THERE HE IS.
SEIZE HIM.

17:26.895 --> 17:27.964
WHO SAID THAT?

17:28.034 --> 17:29.689
UH! HEY! HEY!
OH! OW! NO!

17:29.758 --> 17:30.895
THERE.

17:32.481 --> 17:35.000
[ Groaning ]

17:35.067 --> 17:36.136
WHO AREYOU PEOPLE?

17:36.205 --> 17:37.689
I'M AL GORE, AND THESE

17:37.758 --> 17:40.000
ARE MY VICE-PRESIDENTIAL
ACTION RANGERS

17:40.067 --> 17:42.103
A GROUP OF TOP NERDS
WHOSE SOLE DUTY

17:42.172 --> 17:45.413
IS TO PREVENT DISRUPTIONS
IN THE SPACE-TIME CONTINUUM.

17:45.481 --> 17:48.826
I THOUGHT YOUR SOLE DUTY
WAS TO CAST THE TIE-BREAKING
VOTE IN THE SENATE.

17:48.895 --> 17:51.654
THAT, AND PROTECT
THE SPACE-TIME CONTINUUM.

17:51.723 --> 17:53.067
READ THE CONSTITUTION.

17:53.136 --> 17:55.895
HMM, SO I GUESS YOU'LL WANT
TO SEE MY FRY HOLE.

17:55.964 --> 17:59.136
VERY MUCH SO, BUT FIRST,
MEET THE ACTION RANGERS.

17:59.205 --> 18:01.344
YOU ALREADY KNOW
STEPHEN HAWKING.

18:01.413 --> 18:03.517
ALSO WITH US ARE
NICHELLE NICHOLS

18:03.586 --> 18:05.034
A.K.A. COMMANDER UHURA.

18:05.103 --> 18:08.205
INCOMING TRANSMISSION
FROM MCI ONE-RATE DEPARTMENT.

18:08.275 --> 18:10.205
IT SOUNDS LIKE
A LIMITED-TIME OFFER.

18:10.275 --> 18:11.895
TELL THEM I'M IN THE TUB.

18:11.964 --> 18:14.586
TO MY LEFT,
YOU'LL RECOGNIZE GARY GYGAX

18:14.654 --> 18:16.792
INVENTOR
OF DUNGEONS AND DRAGONS.

18:16.862 --> 18:20.136
GREETINGS. IT'S A...
PLEASURE TO MEET YOU.

18:20.205 --> 18:22.448
AND OUR SUMMER INTERN,
DEEP BLUE

18:22.517 --> 18:25.517
THE WORLD'S FOREMOST
CHESS-PLAYING COMPUTER.

18:25.586 --> 18:26.964
Bishop to knight four.

18:27.034 --> 18:30.103
NOT ALL MISSIONS CAN
BE SOLVED WITH CHESS, DEEP BLUE.

18:30.172 --> 18:31.862
SOMEDAY YOU'LL UNDERSTAND THAT.

18:31.931 --> 18:33.275
WHERE AM I, ANYWAY?

18:33.344 --> 18:35.448
YOU'RE TRAVELING
IN A SPECIALLY EQUIPPED

18:35.517 --> 18:37.103
TERRESTRIAL TRANSPORT MODULE.

18:37.172 --> 18:38.172
A SCHOOL BUS.

18:40.275 --> 18:41.586
SO WHAT DO YOU NERDS WANT?

18:41.654 --> 18:44.448
IT'S ABOUT THAT RIP
IN SPACE-TIME THAT YOU SAW.

18:44.517 --> 18:46.517
I CALL IT A HAWKING HOLE.

18:46.586 --> 18:48.448
NO FAIR--
I SAW IT FIRST.

18:48.517 --> 18:52.103
WHO IS THE JOURNAL OF QUANTUM  PHYSICSGOING TO BELIEVE?

18:52.172 --> 18:55.378
MR. FRY, THE TIME DISRUPTION
INDICATES THAT SOME EVENT

18:55.448 --> 18:59.448
WAS SUPPOSED TO HAPPEN,
BUT DIDN'T DUE TO
A QUANTUM FLUCTUATION.

18:59.517 --> 19:02.344
THAT'S WHY WE HAD TO BEAT YOU
WITH TENNIS RACKETS.

19:02.413 --> 19:05.689
IF WE DON'T GO BACK THERE
AND MAKE THE EVENT HAPPEN

19:05.758 --> 19:08.103
THE ENTIRE UNIVERSE
WILL BE DESTROYED

19:08.172 --> 19:11.964
AND AS AN ENVIRONMENTALIST,
I'M AGAINST THAT.

19:12.034 --> 19:13.758
[ Brakes Squealing ]

19:17.792 --> 19:19.067
SO THEN MY CHAIR TILTED BACK

19:19.136 --> 19:21.240
AND I ALMOST FELL
INTO THIS FREEZER THINGY.

19:21.309 --> 19:23.378
I CALL IT
A HAWKING CHAMBER.

19:23.448 --> 19:25.344
BUT INSTEAD OF FALLING IN
AND GETTING FROZEN

19:25.413 --> 19:26.723
I MISSED AND WANGED MY HEAD.

19:26.792 --> 19:28.758
WELL, IT'S OBVIOUS
WHAT SHOULD HAVE HAPPENED.

19:28.826 --> 19:30.758
THAT WANG TO THE HEAD
SHOULD HAVE KILLED YOU.

19:30.826 --> 19:31.895
UH, WHAT?

19:31.964 --> 19:33.172
LET'S FINISH THE JOB.

19:33.240 --> 19:35.964
NO, WAIT!
THERE MUST BE A PEACEFUL--

19:37.136 --> 19:39.000
HOLD HIM DOWN.Check.

19:41.344 --> 19:42.792
OW! OW!

19:42.862 --> 19:44.240
OW! OW!

19:46.862 --> 19:48.481
WHOA.WHA...?

19:48.550 --> 19:52.103
SOMETHING'S WRONG.
MURDER ISN'T WORKING
AND THAT'S ALL WE'RE GOOD AT.

19:52.172 --> 19:55.586
LET'S TRY SOMETHING ELSE.
MAYBE WE SHOULD...

19:55.654 --> 19:58.309
PUT THE DICE AWAY
BEFORE I TAKE THEM AWAY.

19:58.378 --> 20:00.275
WAIT, I'M GETTING AN IDEA.

20:00.344 --> 20:02.654
WHAT IF FRY WAS
SUPPOSED TO GET FROZEN?

20:02.723 --> 20:03.826
YES.

20:03.895 --> 20:06.586
SHOVE HIM IN THE TUBE.
IT WAS MY IDEA.

20:08.000 --> 20:11.619
HEY, THERE HE IS AGAIN
AND HE BROUGHT NERDS.

20:11.689 --> 20:13.067
TAKE THIS!

20:14.034 --> 20:15.275
GET IN THE TUBE, DUMMY.

20:15.344 --> 20:16.723
WE ONLY HAVE
A FEW SECONDS

20:16.792 --> 20:18.481
BEFORE THE UNIVERSE
IS DESTROYED.

20:21.034 --> 20:22.550
ALL RIGHT,
BUT I NEED A WEAPON

20:22.619 --> 20:24.826
TO FIGHT OFF DRUNKEN ROBOTS
WHEN I WAKE UP.

20:24.895 --> 20:27.240
HERE, TAKE MY
PLUS-ONE MACE.

20:28.034 --> 20:30.826
OKAY, HERE I GO.

20:31.862 --> 20:33.862
[ Maniacal Laughter ]

20:33.931 --> 20:36.240
YOU FOOL!
YOU FOOLISH FOOL!

20:36.309 --> 20:38.654
EH, WHAT'S THE WORST
THING THAT CAN HAPPEN?

20:38.723 --> 20:44.654
[ Screaming ]

20:56.172 --> 20:57.344
GREAT.

20:57.413 --> 20:59.826
THE ENTIRE UNIVERSE
WAS DESTROYED.

20:59.895 --> 21:02.240
DESTROYED?
THEN WHERE ARE WE NOW?

21:02.309 --> 21:04.895
I DON'T KNOW,
BUT I CAN DARN
WELL TELL YOU

21:04.964 --> 21:07.103
WHERE WE'RE NOT--
THE UNIVERSE.

21:07.172 --> 21:08.619
OH, ETERNITY WITH NERDS.

21:08.689 --> 21:11.964
IT'S THE PASADENA STAR TREK
CONVENTION ALL OVER AGAIN.

21:12.034 --> 21:16.826
ANYONE WANT TO PLAY
DUNGEONS AND DRAGONS FOR
THE NEXT QUADRILLION YEARS?

21:16.895 --> 21:18.034
YES, PLEASE.SURE.

21:18.103 --> 21:19.240
Pawn to rook eight.

21:19.309 --> 21:20.895
I'M A TENTH-LEVEL
VICE PRESIDENT.

21:22.964 --> 21:24.895
THAT STORY WAS PREPOSTEROUS.

21:24.964 --> 21:27.034
STEPHEN HAWKING
IN A PIZZERIA.

21:27.103 --> 21:31.103
THIS THING ISN'T WORTH
THE GOLD IT'S MADE OF.

21:31.172 --> 21:34.964
ANYWAY, "THE THING LONGER"
SEEMS TO BE A ROUSING SUCCESS.

21:35.034 --> 21:36.344
GOOD WORK.

21:36.413 --> 21:37.964
[ Amy ]
RIGHT ON, PROFESSOR.

21:40.413 --> 21:42.792
SO THAT'S WHAT THINGS
WOULD BE LIKE

21:42.862 --> 21:44.964
IF I'D INVENTED
"THE THING LONGER."

21:45.034 --> 21:48.378
OH, A MAN CAN DREAM, THOUGH.

21:48.448 --> 21:51.826
A MAN CAN DREAM.
